  "about_the_game": "Explore islands, build shapes, Conquer the puzzles.<br>This is a 3D Sokoban puzzle game.<br>About 130 hand-craft puzzles.<br><br>Features:<br>-A lot of contructing-based puzzle-solving experience.<br>-Each time you pass a level, a block will be generated on the big map, allowing you to build a bridge to reach new level areas.<br>-Each level contains only one key insight. Refuse complex sokoban shuffles.<br>-Playable hint system, get inspired to solve puzzles through mini-levels.<br><br>Join my discord: <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1747510/extras/81179e413c7c5de72e4207c9f84379a5.poster.avif?t=1682941531\" width=524 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1747510/extras/81179e413c7c5de72e4207c9f84379a5.webm?t=1682941531\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1747510/extras/81179e413c7c5de72e4207c9f84379a5.mp4?t=1682941531\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1747510/extras/4187d54cb3954978bb4c9f113c5772b0.poster.avif?t=1682941531\" width=524 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1747510/extras/4187d54cb3954978bb4c9f113c5772b0.webm?t=1682941531\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1747510/extras/4187d54cb3954978bb4c9f113c5772b0.mp4?t=1682941531\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1747510/extras/8a308f9d52e74eea757926781ce09ae8.poster.avi